dct_title_s: Diocese de Rheins et le pais de Rethelpar Jean Jubrien
dct_alternative_sm: Diocese de Rheins et le pais de Rethel / par Jean Jubrien.
dct_description_sm: Decorative title cartouche depicting cupids and a monster face. The scale cartouche depicting dividers and his tools. In the upper right corner of the map two cherubs hold a banner depicting the Reims coat of arms and Rethel coat of arms.
This state was published in atlases by Jan Jansson in 1636, 1637, and 1680.
From the Jansson Appendix Atlas 1636-1680, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan.
